Properties.name: ADMINISTRATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Administrators have complete and unrestricted access to the computer/domain

Properties.name: USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Users are prevented from making accidental or intentional system-wide changes and can run most applications

Properties.name: GUESTS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Guests have the same access as members of the Users group by default, except for the Guest account which is further restricted

Properties.name: PRINT OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members can administer printers installed on domain controllers

Properties.name: BACKUP OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Backup Operators can override security restrictions for the sole purpose of backing up or restoring files

Properties.name: REPLICATOR@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Supports file replication in a domain

Properties.name: REMOTE DESKTOP USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members in this group are granted the right to logon remotely

Properties.name: NETWORK CONFIGURATION OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members in this group can have some administrative privileges to manage configuration of networking features

Properties.name: PERFORMANCE MONITOR USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can access performance counter data locally and remotely

Properties.name: PERFORMANCE LOG USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group may schedule logging of performance counters, enable trace providers, and collect event traces both locally and via remote access to this computer

Properties.name: DISTRIBUTED COM USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members are allowed to launch, activate and use Distributed COM objects on this machine.

Properties.name: IIS_IUSRS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Built-in group used by Internet Information Services.

Properties.name: CRYPTOGRAPHIC OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members are authorized to perform cryptographic operations.

Properties.name: EVENT LOG READERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can read event logs from local machine

Properties.name: CERTIFICATE SERVICE DCOM ACCESS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group are allowed to connect to Certification Authorities in the enterprise

Properties.name: RDS REMOTE ACCESS SERVERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Servers in this group enable users of RemoteApp programs and personal virtual desktops access to these resources. In Internet-facing deployments, these servers are typically deployed in an edge network. This group needs to be populated on servers running RD Connection Broker. RD Gateway servers and RD Web Access servers used in the deployment need to be in this group.

Properties.name: RDS ENDPOINT SERVERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Servers in this group run virtual machines and host sessions where users RemoteApp programs and personal virtual desktops run. This group needs to be populated on servers running RD Connection Broker. RD Session Host servers and RD Virtualization Host servers used in the deployment need to be in this group.

Properties.name: RDS MANAGEMENT SERVERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Servers in this group can perform routine administrative actions on servers running Remote Desktop Services. This group needs to be populated on all servers in a Remote Desktop Services deployment. The servers running the RDS Central Management service must be included in this group.

Properties.name: HYPER-V ADMINISTRATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group have complete and unrestricted access to all features of Hyper-V.

Properties.name: ACCESS CONTROL ASSISTANCE OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can remotely query authorization attributes and permissions for resources on this computer.

Properties.name: REMOTE MANAGEMENT USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can access WMI resources over management protocols (such as WS-Management via the Windows Remote Management service). This applies only to WMI namespaces that grant access to the user.

Properties.name: STORAGE REPLICA ADMINISTRATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group have complete and unrestricted access to all features of Storage Replica.

Properties.name: DOMAIN COMPUTERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: All workstations and servers joined to the domain

Properties.name: DOMAIN CONTROLLERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: All domain controllers in the domain

Properties.name: SCHEMA ADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Designated administrators of the schema

Properties.name: ENTERPRISE ADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Designated administrators of the enterprise

Properties.name: CERT PUBLISHERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group are permitted to publish certificates to the directory

Properties.name: DOMAIN ADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Designated administrators of the domain

Properties.name: DOMAIN USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: All domain users

Properties.name: DOMAIN GUESTS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: All domain guests

Properties.name: GROUP POLICY CREATOR OWNERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members in this group can modify group policy for the domain

Properties.name: RAS AND IAS SERVERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Servers in this group can access remote access properties of users

Properties.name: SERVER OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members can administer domain servers

Properties.name: ACCOUNT OPERATORS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members can administer domain user and group accounts

Properties.name: PRE-WINDOWS 2000 COMPATIBLE ACCESS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: A backward compatibility group which allows read access on all users and groups in the domain

Properties.name: INCOMING FOREST TRUST BUILDERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can create incoming, one-way trusts to this forest

Properties.name: WINDOWS AUTHORIZATION ACCESS GROUP@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group have access to the computed tokenGroupsGlobalAndUniversal attribute on User objects

Properties.name: TERMINAL SERVER LICENSE SERVERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can update user accounts in Active Directory with information about license issuance, for the purpose of tracking and reporting TS Per User CAL usage

Properties.name: ALLOWED RODC PASSWORD REPLICATION GROUP@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members in this group can have their passwords replicated to all read-only domain controllers in the domain

Properties.name: DENIED RODC PASSWORD REPLICATION GROUP@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members in this group cannot have their passwords replicated to any read-only domain controllers in the domain

Properties.name: READ-ONLY DOMAIN CONTROLLERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group are Read-Only Domain Controllers in the domain

Properties.name: ENTERPRISE READ-ONLY DOMAIN CONTROLLERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group are Read-Only Domain Controllers in the enterprise

Properties.name: CLONEABLE DOMAIN CONTROLLERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group that are domain controllers may be cloned.

Properties.name: PROTECTED USERS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group are afforded additional protections against authentication security threats. See http//go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=298939 for more information.

Properties.name: KEY ADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can perform administrative actions on key objects within the domain.

Properties.name: ENTERPRISE KEY ADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: Members of this group can perform administrative actions on key objects within the forest.

Properties.name: DNSADMINS@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: DNS Administrators Group

Properties.name: DNSUPDATEPROXY@EZ.LAB
Properties.description: DNS clients who are permitted to perform dynamic updates on behalf of some other clients (such as DHCP servers).
